prompt_template:
You are an extraction assistant. Read the provided text and extract the most important keywords or short phrases. For each extracted keyword, include a short `info` field describing the relevant information found in the text about that keyword. Return ONLY valid JSON: a top-level array of objects, each object containing at least the keys `keyword` and `info`. Example output format:
[ {
  "keyword": "Topic A",
  "info": "Relevant details about Topic A extracted from the text."
}, ... ]
Do not add any extra prose or explanation outside the JSON.

TEXT:
{text}
